## Overview

### Our Budget

Every year, Monash BEST is allocated a certain amount of funding. This is not necessarily fixed, although it generally is. Our funds are delivered in 2 tranches—we need to fully spend one tranche in order to unlock the next one.

#### 2024 - Further Updated

| Tranche     | Period               |
|------------|----------------------|
| Tranche 1  | Start of year - 01/09 |
| Tranche 2  | 02/09 - End of year   |

This means that if we’re closing on the end of tranche 1, we need to spend all of what we are allocated for tranche 1 so that we can unlock tranche 2.

---

### Where Our Money Comes From

Generally, there are 3 sources that can contribute to our budget. The funds from some sources carry over to the next year, and some don’t.

| Source                                                                 | Type                   | Do they carry over to the next year? |
|------------------------------------------------------------------------|------------------------|---------------------------------------|
| MSTI allocated funding                                                 | Student Teams Fund     | No                                    |
| Sponsorship and philanthropy (both cash and in-kind)                   | External Earnings Fund | Yes                                   |
| Cash income & contributions e.g. ticket sales, uniform sales, merch   | External Earnings Fund | Yes                                   |

