## Non-Coupa Purchases/Requisitions (Reimbursement-based)

### Pros
- Quick, can purchase as soon as approved by Operations Lead.
- Timing not reliant on Monash’s systems.
- Purchaser has full control over when/how to buy.

### Cons
- Purchaser must front their own money.
- Higher financial risk to purchaser if reimbursement fails.
- Reimbursements may take **up to 4 weeks**.

---

### Reimbursement Process

1. Use this link: **[Monash Reimbursement Form](https://docs.google.com/forms/u/1/d/e/1FAIpQLSdvPeQkuUtO95l_EmcWkHEG5Ya0ghz830ZZ6F0zC4Swg8wyCg/viewform?vc=0&c=0&w=1&flr=0)**.
